WEITZ  Trademark Information
 Weitz Investment Management, Inc.
Investment advisory services; Mutual fund investment




Perfect for these industries

Insurance & Financial Services





Words that describe this mark
investment   advisory   services   mutual   fund   investment    
                                    




This is a brand page for the WEITZ trademark by Weitz Investment Management, Inc. 
                                in Omaha, NE, 68124.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this WEITZ trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Weitz Investment Management, Inc. of the WEITZ trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the WEITZ trademark.
                           






On Monday, April 22, 2013,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        WEITZ by 
                        Weitz Investment Management, Inc., Omaha, NE  68124.
                        The USPTO has given the WEITZ 
                        trademark serial  number of  85910462.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for WEITZ is 
                        
                        
                                            PATRICK C. STEPHENSON of 
                                            KUTAK ROCK LLP,  1650 FARNAM ST, OMAHA, NE 68102-2104 
                                .
                            The WEITZ trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for WEITZ 
                            is Investment advisory services; Mutual fund investment. 
                            





